{"ja465:0.1":"Jataka ","ja465:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","ja465:0.3":"Culakunalavagga ","ja465:0.4":"2. Bhaddasalajataka ","ja465:1.1":"“Ka tvam suddhehi vatthehi, ","ja465:1.2":"aghe vehayasam thita; ","ja465:1.3":"Kena tyassuni vattanti, ","ja465:1.4":"kuto tam bhayamagatam”. ","ja465:2.1":"“Taveva deva vijite, ","ja465:2.2":"bhaddasaloti mam vidu; ","ja465:2.3":"Satthi vassasahassani, ","ja465:2.4":"titthato pujitassa me. ","ja465:3.1":"Karayanta nagarani, ","ja465:3.2":"agare ca disampati; ","ja465:3.3":"Vividhe capi pasade, ","ja465:3.4":"na mam te accamannisum; ","ja465:3.5":"Yatheva mam te pujesum, ","ja465:3.6":"tatheva tvampi pujaya”. ","ja465:4.1":"“Tam ivaham na passami, ","ja465:4.2":"thulam kayena te dumam; ","ja465:4.3":"Arohaparinahena, ","ja465:4.4":"abhiruposi jatiya. ","ja465:5.1":"Pasadam karayissami, ","ja465:5.2":"ekatthambham manoramam; ","ja465:5.3":"Tattha tam upanessami, ","ja465:5.4":"ciram te yakkha jivitam”. ","ja465:6.1":"“Evam cittam udapadi, ","ja465:6.2":"sarirena vinabhavo; ","ja465:6.3":"Puthuso mam vikantitva, ","ja465:6.4":"khandaso avakantatha. ","ja465:7.1":"Agge ca chetva majjhe ca, ","ja465:7.2":"paccha mulamhi chindatha; ","ja465:7.3":"Evam me chijjamanassa, ","ja465:7.4":"na dukkham maranam siya”. ","ja465:8.1":"“Hatthapadam yatha chinde, ","ja465:8.2":"Kannanasanca jivato; ","ja465:8.3":"Tato paccha siro chinde, ","ja465:8.4":"Tam dukkham maranam siya. ","ja465:9.1":"Sukham nu khandaso chinnam, ","ja465:9.2":"bhaddasala vanappati; ","ja465:9.3":"Kimhetu kim upadaya, ","ja465:9.4":"khandaso chinnamicchasi”. ","ja465:10.1":"“Yanca hetumupadaya, ","ja465:10.2":"hetum dhammupasamhitam; ","ja465:10.3":"Khandaso chinnamicchami, ","ja465:10.4":"maharaja sunohi me. ","ja465:11.1":"Nati me sukhasamvaddha, ","ja465:11.2":"mama passe nivataja; ","ja465:11.3":"Tepiham upahimseyyam, ","ja465:11.4":"paresam asukhocitam”. ","ja465:12.1":"“Ceteyyarupam cetesi, ","ja465:12.2":"bhaddasala vanappati; ","ja465:12.3":"Hitakamosi natinam, ","ja465:12.4":"abhayam samma dammi te”ti. ","ja465:13.1":"Bhaddasalajatakam dutiyam. "}